headline: NOK (TSE:7240) Valuation in Focus as iPhone 17 Launch Spurs Apple Supplier Optimism
summary: NOK (TSE:7240) drew investor interest this week as early sales of the iPhone 17 series in China and the US surpassed last year's figures. The upbeat demand highlights potential gains for Apple suppliers this quarter. See our latest analysis for NOK.
